(350, '_transient_qsm_sidebar_feed_data', 'a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"link\";s:75:\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/the-best-wordpress-survey-plugins-for-2020/\";s:5:\"title\";s:38:\"Best WordPress Survey Plugins for 2020\";s:11:\"description\";s:188:\"Looking for the Best WordPress Survey Plugin? Want to add a Survey to your WordPress site? Then make sure it is the best in class. Stay tuned we will discuss some of the best free Plugins.\";s:4:\"date\";s:12:\"July 14 2020\";s:6:\"author\";s:13:\"Vikas Singhal\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"link\";s:93:\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/how-to-create-quizzes-using-quiz-builder-plugin-in-wordpress/\";s:5:\"title\";s:61:\"How to Create Quizzes Using Quiz Builder Plugin in WordPress?\";s:11:\"description\";s:319:\"Are you looking for the Best Quiz Builder Plugin for WordPress and are overwhelmed by the options found around you! Well, there might be many plugins that promise to do what they claim, but only a few end up living up to the mark. In this article we discuss about a popular quiz builder plugin - Quiz and Survey Master.\";s:4:\"date\";s:12:\"June 18 2020\";s:6:\"author\";s:12:\"Viraj Narkar\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"link\";s:85:\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/how-to-find-out-what-wordpress-theme-a-site-is-using/\";s:5:\"title\";s:53:\"How to Find out What WordPress Theme a Site Is Using?\";s:11:\"description\";s:378:\"Are you confused about whether that website which you recently visited is using WordPress or not? Well, that&#8217;s relatable. We&#8217;ll help you out. WordPress is a popular and free Content Management System. It is a platform that lets its users create, edit, archive, collaborate, report, publish, and distribute content. Various leading websites use WordPress as [&#8230;]\";s:4:\"date\";s:12:\"June 10 2020\";s:6:\"author\";s:12:\"Viraj Narkar\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"link\";s:85:\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/how-to-create-an-online-exam-or-quiz-during-covid-19/\";s:5:\"title\";s:52:\"How to create an Online Exam or Quiz during COVID-19\";s:11:\"description\";s:294:\"Coronavirus aka. COVID-19 has affected millions around the globe spreading beyond geographical boundaries. And the year 2020 will be remembered as it is going to change our take on the future. Most of the countries are affected by this pandemic and it will take longer for things to get normal.\";s:4:\"date\";s:11:\"May 20 2020\";s:6:\"author\";s:12:\"Viraj Narkar\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"link\";s:75:\"https://quizandsurveymaster.com/create-category-wise-random-questions-quiz/\";s:5:\"title\";s:50:\"How to Create Category wise Random Questions Quiz?\";s:11:\"description\";s:160:\"The latest addition to the QSM plugin brings category wise random questions quiz creation. Allowing you to create a quiz with questions of a particular category\";s:4:\"date\";s:13:\"April 30 2020\";s:6:\"author\";s:12:\"Viraj Narkar\";}}', 'no'),
